latestIgtvVideos.title: What is it like to find, lose and then find love again?💫
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
"Love arrives exactly when it is supposed to! And love leaves exactly when it must."
But how often is it easy to ask love to keep the door open behind when they leave? Would you keep the door open? The next time it enters, does love look the same? Feel the same? Does it sweep you off your feet, yet again? Or does it prefer to enter your life as a companion who'd make simple pleasures of life joyful?
Whatever be the case, make sure you don't wait for anyone to recognise your beauty. You are your own beautiful!
Happy valentine's day🌹

Music by @anuraag_psychaea

latestIgtvVideos.title: Inspired from a little piece I wrote after the Handwara attack.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I could not help but think  about the families of the bravehearts. The courage to accept the uncertainty of a loved one's life is just unimaginable. For those undying spirits, I pray and hope for more strength and respect to the families of our martyrs and the soldiers who still continue to risk their lives.🙏

An acquaintance, after reading the piece confessed that one of the martyrs was his friend who had married just about two years ago.
In this piece, I have tried to attempt 'Karuna rasa' (something that's quite out of my comfort zone🙈) portraying the anguish due to loss of a loved one.
.
Original song by @shafqatamanata 
Tabla cover by @bang.it.paaji 
(a collaboration requested by @_puneetkaur_ 😌)
.
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Let's do our bit🌸
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I fell in love with this piece and was reminded of all those times when my mother ran downstairs to serve cold coffee/neembu paani to the sanitization wokers in our society.

Tried to create a mime act on this beautiful collaboration of such wonderful artists.! .
Voice : @rajkummar_rao
Sound : @patranimacchi
Words by @iamparitoshtripathi

Also, a huge shoutout to @deepakyatri sir for introducing me to mime acting ! Thank you for your guidance.
